  <title>GLib.Source.prototype.get_ready_time</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function get_ready_time(): Number(gint64) {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_source_get_ready_time()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Gets the "ready time" of <code>source</code>, as set by
<link xref="GLib.Source.set_ready_time"/>.</p>  <p>Any time before the current monotonic time (including 0) is an
indication that the source will fire immediately.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the monotonic ready time, -1 for "never"</p>
</item>
